{"tid":2160630,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚午 越萊 買蘋果日報送雞翼","createTime":"2020-08-17T05:41:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T12:40:37.000Z","uid":310853,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8979944a4ae536dc963814a012e6cb9738a27618","tid":2160630,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T05:41:28.000Z","msg":"話說小弟又睇到有巴打提及一間越南食店<br />\n之後就心郁郁想試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4UZjdNX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4UZjdNX.png&h=a2541b36&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oQ7wPm2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoQ7wPm2.png&h=420e45ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nD食物又真係唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9DFVwBb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9DFVwBb.png&h=69fdebde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n單拼就$36 不過我加多$8要埋個炸蝦餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eVCT2Jt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeVCT2Jt.png&h=09083a7e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/66hppXd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F66hppXd.png&h=67b50184&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z6xdihn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ6xdihn.png&h=b7e0330d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依份就係蘋果日報送嘅雞翼 味道唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢會係你份蘋果日報上面吸個印<br />\n送雞翼或者春卷 不過我就揀雞翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suKORC7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuKORC7.png&h=c84128cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後我額外再加多個蝦丸<br />\n咬落去真係彈嘅 唔係淋身嗰d<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sSLZdSq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsSLZdSq.png&h=563c4681&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JMtcySv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJMtcySv.png&h=84ca613d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後我留意到 佢蒜香牛油雞翼$18 3隻<br />\n姐係$6 隻 買份蘋果有兩隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等我下次有機會試埋個牛肉粉先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"981b471510d09b7435b8f01bdf9cb27e37305943","tid":2160630,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T05:43:52.000Z","msg":"撈檬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93c009471da131ee710dfb9a28f38b5f39732d70","tid":2160630,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T05:43:55.000Z","msg":"post 地址加fb/ig(如有) and pin plz<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"795a6421b52b241f6916ab00bbe56a1fb5308311","tid":2160630,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"981b471510d09b7435b8f01bdf9cb27e37305943","tid":2160630,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T05:43:52.000Z","msg":"撈檬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T05:44:55.000Z","msg":"Yes 幾好食"},{"pid":"9c5307ca8b84d226b8cd825cdc2e082eefd71271","tid":2160630,"uid":310853,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"93c009471da131ee710dfb9a28f38b5f39732d70","tid":2160630,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T05:43:55.000Z","msg":"post 地址加fb/ig(如有) and pin plz<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T05:50:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UjiTirj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-